#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:4
msgid "Trainers Training Program"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:6
msgid ""
"This outline represents the time commitment required for being an "
"instructor Trainer with the Carpentries. Please read through and check to"
" see that you are able to commit to the responsibilities outlined below."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:8
msgid ""
"Instructor Trainers agree to abide by the Code of Conduct in all "
"communications and interactions with The Carpentries community."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:10
msgid ""
"Read How Learning Works by Susan Ambrose and discuss in book club format "
"with Trainers-in-training. Preliminary reading schedule."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:11
msgid ""
"Time commitment: 1 hour per week for 8 weeks meetings; can miss one "
"meeting; ~10 hours reading"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:12
msgid "Join Trainer meetings"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:13
msgid "Time commitment: 1 hour per month; can miss one meeting"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:14
msgid "Shadow a teaching demonstration session"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:15
msgid "Time commitment: 1 hour one time"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:16
msgid "Shadow at least half a day of an online instructor training event"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:17
msgid "Time commitment: 4 hours one time"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:18
msgid ""
"Teach once either online or in person with experienced Trainer (after "
"finishing book club)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:19
msgid "Time commitment: 2 days one time plus prep"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:20
msgid "Agree to the Trainer Agreement."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:22
msgid ""
"Total time commitment for continuing Trainers: 4 days per year + 2.5 hrs "
"per month"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:25
msgid ""
"Total time commitment for new Trainers: 3 days + ~30 hours over 3 month "
"period, including reading and prep time"
msgstr ""

