msgid ""
"For the most recent Trainer Training schedule and discussion questions, "
"see the Trainer Training Curriculum"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:32
msgid "Reviewing New Trainer Applications"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:34
msgid ""
"Director of Instructor Training and Carpentries staff will decide on "
"goals for Trainer recruitment."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:35
msgid "Trainer Application will be modified to reflect these goals."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:36
msgid ""
"Open application period will be announced via Carpentries platforms "
"including Twitter, Facebook, the Discuss email list, and blogs. Ask "
"relevant community members to promote within their networks as well.  "
"Personal invitations can be sent with this email template."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:37
msgid "Ensure communication emphasizes overall goals."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:38
msgid ""
"Ask 2-3 existing Trainers to help review applications in line with "
"defined goals. There is no rubric for this.  Reviewers should leave notes"
" supporting their rankings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:39
msgid ""
"Consolidate rankings, adding discretionary points for gaps in "
"representation by characteristics like gender, race, geography, and "
"experience."
msgstr ""

